'''ᱚᱨᱱᱟ.ᱵ ᱨᱚᱱᱡᱚᱱ ᱜᱚᱥᱣᱟᱢᱤ''' ( ᱟᱥᱟᱢᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱺ￼￼অৰ্ণৱ ৰঞ্জন গোস্বামী ), ( ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱙ ᱚᱠᱴᱩᱵᱚᱨ ᱑᱙᱗᱓ ) ᱫᱚ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱮᱡ ᱱᱟᱜᱚᱨᱤᱠ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱜᱤᱥᱣᱟᱢᱤ ᱫᱚ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟ ᱡᱚᱨᱱᱟᱞᱤᱥᱴ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱟᱨ ᱴᱮᱞᱤᱵᱦᱤᱡᱚᱱ ᱱᱮᱣᱡ ᱯᱨᱮᱥᱮᱱᱴᱚᱨ ᱟᱨ ᱮᱱᱠᱚᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱩᱱᱤ ᱫᱚ '''ᱨᱤᱯᱚᱵᱞᱤᱠ ᱴᱤᱵᱦᱤ''' ᱤᱡ ᱢᱮᱱᱮᱡᱤᱝ ᱰᱟᱭᱨᱮᱠᱴᱚᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱟᱨ ᱩᱱᱤ '''ᱨᱟᱡᱤᱤᱵ ᱪᱚᱱᱫᱨᱚᱥᱮᱠᱦᱟ.ᱨ''' ᱥᱟᱞᱟᱜ ᱛᱮ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱪᱮᱱᱮᱞ ᱠᱡᱩᱞᱟ ᱠᱮᱟᱠᱤᱱ ᱾<ref>http://indianexpress.com/article/india/nda-mp-rajeev-chandrasekhar-investor-director-in-arnab-goswami-channel/</ref><ref name="indianexpress1">[http://businessworld.in/article/Arnab-Goswami-s-Republic-TV-To-Launch-On-6-May/05-05-2017-117680/ Arnab Goswami resigns as Editor-in Chief of Times Now | The Indian Express<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>   

ᱜᱚᱥᱣᱟᱢᱤ ᱫᱚ ᱒᱐᱐᱖ ᱠᱦᱚᱱ ᱒᱐᱑᱖ ᱦᱚᱵᱤᱡ ᱛᱮ '''ᱴᱟᱤᱢᱥ ᱱᱟᱣ''' ᱟᱨ '''ᱤᱴ ᱱᱟᱣ''' ᱤᱡ ᱱᱤᱣᱡ ᱮᱱᱠᱚᱨ ᱮ ᱛᱟᱦᱮ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾<ref>{{cite web|author=Arundhati Roy |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2008/dec/12/mumbai-arundhati-roy |title=Arundhati Roy: Mumbai was not India's 9/11 &#124; World news |publisher=theguardian.com |date= |accessdate=31 January 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.exchange4media.com/54312_television-news-will-dominate-50-of-the-revenues-arnab-goswami.html |title=Television news will dominate 50% of the revenues: Arnab Goswami. |publisher=Exchange4media.com |date=22 January 2014 |accessdate=31 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203025509/http://www.exchange4media.com/54312_television-news-will-dominate-50-of-the-revenues-arnab-goswami.html |archivedate=3 February 2014 |df=dmy }}</ref> ᱴᱟᱤᱢᱥ ᱱᱟᱣ ᱨᱮ ᱟᱡ ᱫᱚ, ᱥᱚᱱᱤᱵᱟᱨ ᱟᱨ ᱨᱚᱵᱤᱵᱟᱨ ᱪᱦᱚᱲᱚ ᱡᱦᱚᱛᱚ ᱫᱤᱱ, ᱟᱭᱩᱵ ᱙ ᱵᱚᱡᱮ ''ᱫᱟ. ᱱᱤᱣᱡᱟᱣᱟᱨ'' ᱨᱮ ᱞᱟᱤᱵ ᱰᱤᱵᱮᱛ ᱮ ᱠᱚᱨᱚᱣᱮᱫ ᱴᱟᱦᱮᱡ ᱾<ref>{{cite web|author=Anuradha Raman |url=http://www.outlookindia.com/article/Wrecking-News/293690 |title=Wrecking News}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Hartosh Singh Bal |url=http://www.outlookindia.com/article/The-Arnab-Cast-Of-Characters/293692 |title=The Arnab Cast of Characters}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Shahjahan Madampat |url=http://www.outlookindia.com/article/The-Nation-Will-Skewer-You-Now/293693 |title=The Nation Will Skewer You Now}}</ref> ᱩᱱᱤ ᱫᱚ ''ᱯᱦᱨᱟᱱᱠᱞᱤ ᱥᱯᱤᱠᱤᱝ ᱣᱤᱴᱦ ᱟᱨᱱᱚᱵ'' ᱮ ᱦᱚᱥᱛ ᱞᱮᱟᱭ ᱾<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Rahul-Gandhis-first-interview-Full-text/articleshow/29455665.cms |title=Rahul Gandhi's first interview: Full text – Times Of India |publisher=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=27 January 2014 |accessdate=31 January 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://blogs.wsj.com/indiarealtime/2014/01/27/the-gandhi-goswami-smackdown/ |title=The Gandhi-Goswami Smackdown – India Real Time – WSJ |publisher=Blogs.wsj.com |date=27 January 2014 |accessdate=31 January 2014}}</ref> ᱑ ᱱᱚᱵᱦᱮᱢᱵᱚᱨ ᱒᱐᱑᱖ ᱨᱮ, ᱜᱚᱥᱣᱟᱢᱤ ᱫᱚ '''ᱴᱟᱤᱢᱥ ᱱᱟᱣ''' ᱠᱦᱚᱱ ᱠᱟᱢᱤ ᱵᱟᱜᱤ ᱠᱮᱟᱭ ᱾<ref name="indianexpress1"/><ref>http://www.openthemagazine.com/shorts/smallworld/arnab-goswami-india-s-inquisitor</ref> ᱟᱡᱟᱜᱽ ᱱᱟᱣᱟ ᱪᱮᱱᱮᱞ ᱨᱤᱯᱚᱵᱞᱤᱠ ᱴᱤᱵᱦᱤ ᱫᱚ ᱖ ᱢᱮᱭ ᱒᱐᱑᱗ ᱮᱨ ᱚᱰᱚᱠ ᱮᱱᱟ ᱾<ref>{{cite web|title=Arnab Goswami's Republic TV launched; here's how to watch it live on phone|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/arnab-goswami-s-republic-tv-launched-here-s-how-to-watch-it-live-on-phone-117050600230_1.html|publisher=Business Standard, India.|accessdate=6 May 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Arnab Goswami's Republic first Indian news channel to air live on Hotstar|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/arnab-goswami-s-republic-first-indian-news-channel-to-air-live-on-hotstar-117050500303_1.html|publisher=Business Standard, India.|accessdate=6 May 2017}}</ref>

